%% description: User login with validation and error handling.

flowchart TD
    START([Open Login Page]) --> VALIDATE[Validate Credentials]
    VALIDATE -->|Valid| AUTH{MFA Required?}
    VALIDATE -->|Invalid| ERR[Show Error Message]
    AUTH -->|Yes| MFA[Send OTP / Prompt MFA]
    AUTH -->|No| SESSION[Create Session]
    MFA -->|Success| SESSION
    MFA -->|Fail| ERR
    SESSION --> DASH([Redirect to Dashboard])
